snippet.title: Mobile Suit Gundam: Silver Phantom - Official Trailer | UploadVR Showcase Winter 2023
snippet.description: Get a peek at Mobile Suit Gundam: Silver Phantom, an upcoming narrative interactive VR experience set in the Gundam universe. Join Kiichiro Inoue from Sunrise Studio at Bandai Namco Filmworks for a message regarding this upcoming VR game. Mobile Suit Gundam: Silver Phantom is coming to Meta Quest.
